title: Clothes Appear To Be Optional For Elle Johnson When She Snowboards
text:
TOP 5437328 
Instagram superstar and sports model Elle Johnson apparently likes to snowboard in nothing but a small bikini. 
The blonde bombshell posted a photo of herself on the slopes with a revealing bikini and the caption, “My version of the #MondayBlues. #mondaymotivation.” (SLIDESHOW: Abigail Ratchford Is Barely Wearing Anything In These Photos) 
— Elle Johnson (@_ElleJohnson) January 23, 2017 
I’m not a marketing expert, but I have a feeling this would be a great way to drive foot traffic to your ski resort. (SLIDESHOW: THIS BLONDE BOMBSHELL MIGHT BE THE HOTTEST MODEL ON INSTAGRAM) 
Her Instagram alone could provide plenty of material that could sell some tickets for the mountain. Click an image below for larger version.
